Data Science is an interdisciplinary field that uses statistical methods, to extract actionable insights from  data.

## Descriptive Statistics
Descriptive statistics are quantitative techniques used to summarize, organize, and describe the main features of a dataset.
![Descriptive stats](/assets/Descriptivestats.jpg)

## Inferential Statistics
Inferential statistics are statistical methods used to draw conclusions about a population based on data collected from a sample.
